##Method void unflatten(SkReadBuffer&) #unflatten

#Method populates a paint, typically from a serialized stream, created by calling
#flatten at an earlier time.

The #SkReadBuffer class is not public, so #Method cannot be meaningfully called
by a Skia client.

# why is #Method public? bug.skia.org/6172

