##Method void reset() #reset

Set all paint's contents to their initial values. This is equivalent to replacing
the paint by calling #empty_constructor.

##Example
SkPaint paint1, paint2;
paint1.setColor(SK_ColorRED);
paint1.reset();
SkDebugf("paint1 %c= paint2", paint1 == paint2 ? '=' : '!');
##Example ##

##StdOut
paint1 == paint2
##StdOut ##

